{"tid":1790831,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"【再開過】由連登開始嘅連寵拯救隊上線啦！","createTime":"2019-12-20T09:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T23:58:02.000Z","uid":777,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"53d15fe0704eb6478d16b48a8a89d23c7eaec289","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DZwyUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DZwyUY.jpg&h=67f65dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連寵已經一個月，<br />\n都未好正式咁介紹自己！<br />\n等我地簡單而隆重咁同大家打個招呼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[正經mode on]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋Facebook <a href=\"http://fb.me/petwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fpetwithyou&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=9da4ab7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/petwithyou</a><br />\n我哋Instagram  @petwithyouhk<br />\n我哋TG Channel <a href=\"https://t.me/petwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpetwithyou&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=d27d4244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/petwithyou</a><br />\n我哋TG 公海Group <a href=\"http://t.me/petwithyoudiss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpetwithyoudiss&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=e2901c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/petwithyoudiss</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本義工團隊透過連登討論區聚集而來，<br />\n祈望香港動保界發展得更好。<br />\n我們基於相互尊重及溝通的原則，<br />\n希望減少棄養及讓大眾更願意領養動物。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">*<br />\n「連寵拯救隊」團隊亦已獲LIHKG論壇正式書面回覆，<br />\n表示名稱及設計並沒有抄襲 / 冒認討論區之嫌，<br />\n因此可正式使用該名稱。</span><br />\n<br />\n願景：<br />\n1. 拯救受傷或被遺棄動物。<br />\n2. 執行及推動社區動物絕育放回。<br />\n3. 持續招募及訓練義工，擴大後援團隊。<br />\n4. 宣揚善待動物及推廣領養。<br />\n5. 建立黃色動物聯盟及供應鏈，團結更多黃色動保團體與商戶。<br />\n6. 開展黃色非牟利事業，協助手足們自力更生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「連寵拯救隊」承諾：<br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n加強與領養人的交流溝通，<br />\n分享正確飼養動物方法及日常護理方法，<br />\n從而減少拒絕領養申請的情況，<br />\n務求令更多毛孩獲得領養。<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n欣賞不同人的價值，歡迎從事不同行業的手足，<br />\n各施所長，一起參與動保工作。<br />\n<br />\n3. <br />\n尊重生命，不論毛孩年紀疾病均會盡力拯救。<br />\n<br />\n4.<br />\n 在確保毛孩在安全及良好的環境成長的大前提下，<br />\n改良領養手續程序。以尊重溝通為基礎，<br />\n保護動物生命為重心，強調與領養人溝通 ，<br />\n令過程更人性化，以免嚇怕新手主人。<br />\n<br />\n5. <br />\n所有物資捐贈、捐款及財政狀況均公開透明並定期公佈。<br />\n<br />\n#連寵拯救隊<br />\n#與手足並肩<br />\n#與毛孩同行"},{"pid":"63919a3b4169ae84920c88e6504ed7735e96d14a","tid":1790831,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:52:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e10ea8886928fc6656ce1c250a5af1b04fc35ed3","tid":1790831,"uid":150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8a44315085b18b20a00be3aead5c23b3f765d8","tid":1790831,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"想加入有無人工"},{"pid":"9805b8461f841c5b62a6f99ac8ad4903863c786f","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aa8a44315085b18b20a00be3aead5c23b3f765d8","tid":1790831,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"想加入有無人工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"全部自發義工，何來人工"},{"pid":"0457c1a044bdd50dd5d1a237732fbf7808201930","tid":1790831,"uid":91605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"546bd45161062f09103153f117bd1e063ba61471","tid":1790831,"uid":155853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:34:57.000Z","msg":"好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e16e30c3e1579949d63441e84966ef8a898409","tid":1790831,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:11:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4a9816accb79ecb1990ee2a743e99526be3bf79","tid":1790831,"uid":296866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:12:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6f73753eb912b779502b20d5e4783c03e30b46","tid":1790831,"uid":31524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ecb19b050d470373e5c0d9e224ed8b9064f8218","tid":1790831,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T15:29:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b4a4c1d7f41d624c7978d7d1ad738b8c0bfa029a","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ac7168d378f6629e2c16f8134a1d5d3b1df04b","tid":1790831,"uid":77598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fdc0881dfad738d5300f32bb3bd18972a89abb","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"🙋🏻召喚租盤🙋🏻<br />\n<br />\n隨住越黎越多貓主子進駐連寵等待奴才，我地都密鑼緊鼓要搵更大既地方令佢地住得更安心舒服☺<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有平而有合適既地方（要有Toilet）甚或免費租盤，請聯絡我哋🙇🏻🙇🏻<br />\n<br />\n就更可以減輕我地現時既資金短缺嘅問題🙏🏼<br />\n<br />\n咁我地就可以盡早安排搬遷🏃🏿&zwj;♀畀一個5星級既地方畀主子同更多需要幫忙嘅浪浪🐱<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家🙇🏻<br />\n<br />\nadmin @fkyouhk_gov @diu7popolomo"},{"pid":"2c85d2622e16a5a2bd84dcf450cf983ee0fc0071","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65a2433c7f45b480a5c1cfc26b8b50ed7f5c538f","tid":1790831,"uid":154143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T23:41:27.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1e454de0ab4088c86bf097437577cc5eace520","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:38:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd6c102281b13c3e9c7b3a63d899a66a54319b07","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T00:00:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"857422ea2e46ae7ed47891fc14067e3321fea153","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab52e2cf07755970fd520e4948145276f6ea73e6","tid":1790831,"uid":150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c571402398e8ac1adf5def27ab069540986ad52d","tid":1790831,"uid":94449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n支持呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3adc1cf0eba0dbac8f7641fd9e7ecf2218082aab","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T01:54:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07ebfe193251cb005d5b42a022c593616b82a30c","tid":1790831,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"你地出領養會唔會好似啲出面貓異工咁，查完家宅又要家訪，又嫌呢樣又嫌個樣咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1043cafcbd2b56099238827f678d7d754e93092","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07ebfe193251cb005d5b42a022c593616b82a30c","tid":1790831,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"你地出領養會唔會好似啲出面貓異工咁，查完家宅又要家訪，又嫌呢樣又嫌個樣咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"你有睇過我哋fb同ig就知唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你有睇過我喺其他Post嘅留言就會更加知道點解<br />\n<br />\n第一，我哋係用waiting list形式<br />\n你先提供你喜歡嘅條件，我地揀人時你亦有權揀貓<br />\n到真係有貓出嘅時候我哋就會按你填嘅嘢match up<br />\n基本上我哋會睇咗你填嘅嘢先<br />\n85%肯定先會搵你傾計兼上我哋度探貓<br />\n傾過計覺得你真係好合適先會搞家居上嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc073a6899bb7b3dc1e695f0b76a25c0e41190b8","tid":1790831,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:16:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5d75af474d685400fc230447f603d7420f56b7e1","tid":1790831,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1043cafcbd2b56099238827f678d7d754e93092","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07ebfe193251cb005d5b42a022c593616b82a30c","tid":1790831,"uid":22560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:21:26.000Z","msg":"你地出領養會唔會好似啲出面貓異工咁，查完家宅又要家訪，又嫌呢樣又嫌個樣咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:15:07.000Z","msg":"你有睇過我哋fb同ig就知唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你有睇過我喺其他Post嘅留言就會更加知道點解<br />\n<br />\n第一，我哋係用waiting list形式<br />\n你先提供你喜歡嘅條件，我地揀人時你亦有權揀貓<br />\n到真係有貓出嘅時候我哋就會按你填嘅嘢match up<br />\n基本上我哋會睇咗你填嘅嘢先<br />\n85%肯定先會搵你傾計兼上我哋度探貓<br />\n傾過計覺得你真係好合適先會搞家居上嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"係就好啦，多謝你答得我咁詳細<br />\n我好怕嗰啲貓義工當正領養者係犯咁審<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我會慢慢睇你地ig 同fb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc0c799c4e61a9c76fdb14822de51bcff125279","tid":1790831,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T18:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dcbca9ff1b25b5eca5c352ec95ddac54f4be786","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce79d28b2bdf24cf5ae645ea3ef701d49635ec6","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"嚟緊2020❣️<br />\n<br />\n連寵第一大件事係搬遷地方解決飽和貓舍宿位問題😕<br />\n<br />\n目前盈餘絕對不足我哋交按金與搬遷<br />\n<br />\n因此我哋正進行及會繼續義賣，希望大家多多支持 <br />\n<br />\n想直接支持我哋嘅請聯絡 @fkyouhk_gov @hkvetnurse <br />\n<br />\n我哋預計租金會控制喺一萬內<br />\n預期整個搬遷費用會在五萬內（包括兩月租金，間隔房間，按金，籠與物資購置等等）<br />\n<br />\n所有收支會喺搬遷完成後詳細列出<br />\n<br />\n希望換咗場地後會多咗空間容納更加多嘅流浪動物（有十幾隻等緊位😢）同埋更加多嘅義工可以上嚟學習照顧<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家！新年快樂！<br />\n<br />\n#與毛孩同行 #與手足並肩 <br />\n#連寵拯救隊"},{"pid":"7e7800a45063c4cc66610acd143ff1bcaf496054","tid":1790831,"uid":11013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=9ed05d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"cb4884d607088e509722e19d16932fcd4582c17b","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb59a83f575b1eb8f3016efa1d8ff5a64b720acf","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"【聲明】<br />\n<br />\n連寵拯救隊（下稱連寵），對有人誣蔑本團隊指連寵以他人身份眾籌醫療費貓隻費用一事，深表遺憾並予以譴責，在此作出以下聲明：<br />\n<br />\n事件起因原帖<br />\n《求資助貓仔做手術》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802066</a><br />\n<br />\n上述帖子樓主「小新隻狗」並非連寵團隊成員，亦與連寵團隊成員並無任何關係。<br />\n<br />\n事件經過如下：<br />\n<br />\n樓主於連登發帖表示拾獲一貓，發現四肢皆斷，經前後兩位醫生診症後，終獲口頭報價4萬5千元手術費。未能承擔費用因此網上眾籌。<br />\n<br />\n及後，有人留言（詳見#11留言），貼上本團隊之Telegram公海討論區連結，示意樓主入谷宣傳其眾籌計劃。<br />\n<br />\n樓主進入Telegram討論公海後，直接再次交代上述帖子事宜，但並無聯絡任何連寵群組管理員。而管理員發現後亦即時了解事件，包括詢問種種未有交代之疑團。經了解亦表示拒絕進行眾籌協助，原因為貓隻是樓主自己想繼續飼養之寵物，因此不再是「浪浪」，故樓主本人應負起主人責任去醫治寵物，不應眾籌。如未能負責費用，便不應自私，應以貓貓身體健康為重，交予信任機構進行醫治和拯救。<br />\n<br />\n及後，Telegram公海群組繼續就有關事件討論，連寵管理員亦有聯絡毛守查詢事件進度。了解後亦有向公海群組各人轉達毛守方面的回應。事件亦於群組漸漸告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n直至31日早上，Telegram群組突然有一成員「Anthony Cheung」（下稱A）加入，言行之間亦直接指連寵成員為樓主同一人，其他在群組已久的人亦表示A誤會，可惜A一意孤行，不聽眾人之言，更表示其他會員與整個連寵團隊都是樓主同一人。<br />\n<br />\n本來此等無稽之談，連寵亦只一笑置之。可惜A變本加厲，繼續在Telegram公海群組擾亂秩序，一次又一次誣蔑本團隊。更在毫無根據的情況下，指控本團隊其中一名成員，為上述帖子中，貓貓曾光顧之獸醫診所姑娘，並誹謗成員蓄意刪改X光片，看診收據。<br />\n<br />\nA亦繼續在Telegram公海群組及私人對話中多番表示「大把時間搞你地」、「玩大佢」。肆意恐嚇成員。及後更明目張膽，再於連登討論區多番發表不同大字標題本團隊名字之惡意文章。對於在毫無證據，完全捏造情況下，顛倒是非黑白，刻意抹黑連寵拯救隊，並作出失實陳述，連寵表示十分憤慨，亦將向連登討論區索取有關失實誹謗之帖子資料，保留法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦鼓勵有疑慮，對事件關心的朋友，可以到以下連結，翻查Telegram公海群組所有對話紀錄。亦可向帖子內提及有關團隊及診所查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/petwithyoudiss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpetwithyoudiss&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5U6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=e2901c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/petwithyoudiss</a><br />\n<br />\n我們堅持做實事，不妄語，堅守原則。<br />\n但不代表我們怕事，可以被人任意欺負。<br />\n<br />\n與手足並肩，與毛孩同行。<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港，感謝大家，新年快樂。<br />\n<br />\n連寵拯救隊<br />\n2019年12月31日"},{"pid":"799e738a23f7f567aca219bdccfdaadcec36c3d4","tid":1790831,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T15:35:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"553b4d5440783884fd6ecfa2d719013373ed2d5f","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾黑警"},{"pid":"09d8149a326b560bb033a2039df80e92de6121fc","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfcoC8s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfcoC8s.jpg&h=fe99cb01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDAah8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDAah8t.jpg&h=e7f7e6d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【12月份報表】<br />\n<br />\n今期租金成員自己夾咗🙈<br />\n物資捐助都非常多人支持真係好感激你哋🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n不過罐罐真係去得太快🙈仍然需要大家嘅幫忙<br />\n另外就係大家都見到盈餘<br />\n之前都講過係絕對唔足夠去應付新場地🤒<br />\n希望大家可以幫手😢今個星期開始我哋就會去睇新場地嘅地方。佢望可以快啲令到等緊上貓舍嘅貓貓快啲有個Shelter🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n物資捐助tg @nggjm9 @mello0v0<br />\n捐款贊助tg @fkyouhk_gov @hkvetnurse"},{"pid":"3492ff71ff90f6f450cb697156a3a9969b3bdabe","tid":1790831,"uid":229656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:43:23.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aa793e670197ff0396a4d8da172079cd1529d8","tid":1790831,"uid":260004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b598c24d6616128e38c12a606cab6e1775acb00b","tid":1790831,"uid":306940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:54:06.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"100c2dd695bccbba2cdf7292a8b758d28bfecd58","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T00:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e115fabc79388932d630ae9252d19f3b667118","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fef3493b60f5d07d022864f7f9ee74ec06fe920","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a74c974f2e0e74f6266ba986523ce4348316c8","tid":1790831,"uid":245896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ed2ea985344a396e517f861a2113492f0a4f45","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T23:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7TvxHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7TvxHi.jpg&h=6e25b212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【連寵第一個領養人上線啦❣️】<br />\n<br />\n話咁快豬太郎就乖豬完成訓練<br />\n可以去新主人屋企啦<br />\n經過我哋配對之後🎊<br />\n就幫到佢搵新主人啦<br />\n點知係我哋同新主人傾吓計<br />\n再睇埋屋企環境嘅時候<br />\n豬太郎竟然靜悄悄咁樣⋯⋯<br />\n同靜香去到談婚論嫁嘅地步🤭🤭🤭<br />\n呢個時候我哋梗係打蛇隨棍上嫁埋個女啦🤣🤣🤣<br />\n豬爸爸又非常好咁樣接納埋呢個新抱🤣<br />\n所以就係咁我哋連寵第一對貓就正式一齊去咗新屋企啦🎊🤗<br />\n喺度祝願豬太郎同靜香同新屋企人幸福愉快🥰🥰<br />\n好人好貓一生平安❣️<br />\n<br />\n*豬太郎已絕育，靜香則稍後由領養人帶往絕育<br />\n<br />\n#連寵寶寶 #靜香 #豬太郎 #領養"},{"pid":"4259f0b5d3d3dabfcafe1477ed808c0c8c4866f0","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836a2f8401792871d1553fb82523efd54c9fe6a4","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc308216d6b2fabe5a13058c1fccfa51a2b2ebdc","tid":1790831,"uid":54901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T14:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beef3a624a1d2df5b31c25a4884b45d646508287","tid":1790831,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:55:14.000Z","msg":"啲揮春又畫得幾靚"},{"pid":"bf713f0c338589d270ce6a8390c21766160bb5d7","tid":1790831,"uid":221090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"想幫手做義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb09e293df5f34e697e9f2ddfd6d81d5206387c","tid":1790831,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T17:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d337c48d1431c9515823a18d1ca1ddaa2f7267","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T23:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZUvkp8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZUvkp8.jpg&h=e42cb5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【拾貮有家了❣️】<br />\n<br />\n小12真係好受歡迎🙈<br />\n乖嘅女孩子就係多人錫<br />\n12嘅新主人係多分面都係100分<br />\n<br />\n點解咁講😂<br />\n佢為咗12，日日上貓舍做義工啦<br />\n為咗12仲自己舉手一齊帶12打針<br />\n為咗12佢係公開接受申請時9秒9填表<br />\n為咗12拆咗屋企個窗花整網再上返<br />\n<br />\n仲買左全粉紅色用具<br />\n彌補返一直係貓舍俾人當男仔嘅日子。<br />\n<br />\n🙈所以就係咁，12有新主人了<br />\n希望小12同幾位婆婆級家姐開心快樂❣️<br />\n<br />\n#好人好貓一生平安<br />\n#連寵寶寶 #拾貮 #與手足並肩<br />\n#與毛孩同行"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e2ed2ea985344a396e517f861a2113492f0a4f45","tid":1790831,"uid":777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T23:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7TvxHi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7TvxHi.jpg&h=6e25b212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【連寵第一個領養人上線啦❣️】<br />\n<br />\n話咁快豬太郎就乖豬完成訓練<br />\n可以去新主人屋企啦<br />\n經過我哋配對之後🎊<br />\n就幫到佢搵新主人啦<br />\n點知係我哋同新主人傾吓計<br />\n再睇埋屋企環境嘅時候<br />\n豬太郎竟然靜悄悄咁樣⋯⋯<br />\n同靜香去到談婚論嫁嘅地步🤭🤭🤭<br />\n呢個時候我哋梗係打蛇隨棍上嫁埋個女啦🤣🤣🤣<br />\n豬爸爸又非常好咁樣接納埋呢個新抱🤣<br />\n所以就係咁我哋連寵第一對貓就正式一齊去咗新屋企啦🎊🤗<br />\n喺度祝願豬太郎同靜香同新屋企人幸福愉快🥰🥰<br />\n好人好貓一生平安❣️<br />\n<br />\n*豬太郎已絕育，靜香則稍後由領養人帶往絕育<br />\n<br />\n#連寵寶寶 #靜香 #豬太郎 #領養"}}